6371 - Pension, Health and Welfare Funds Summary > ENERGY INDUSTRIES SUPERANNUATION SCHEME PTY LIMITED is an Australian proprietary company. Its operations cover pension, health and welfare funds. The company is not involved in the import or export of goods. ENERGY INDUSTRIES SUPERANNUATION SCHEME PTY LIMITED is headquartered in Perth, Western Australia. It is headed by director Guy Chalkley. For the 2023 financial year, the company reported revenue of $37.06 million. Its net profit totalled $1.91 million. ENERGY INDUSTRIES SUPERANNUATION SCHEME PTY LIMITED forms part of the finance, insurance, and real estate industry sector. Key Personnel > No key personnel were found for the selected company.
